| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4413 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d1a4a164-8b1c-5b7d-a12a-3f78bc6ba7cf"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
